name: Flouring Age VI
additionalNotes:
This cigar is listed in the Cigarcyclopedia http://www.cigarcyclopedia.com/webapp/images/stories/cigarcyclopedia/10_handmade_g-111409.pdf

It's manufactured in Sichuan, China and the filler is grown in China.

One other thing on the wrappers...the Indonesian wrapper is grown in Sumatra according the Cigarcyclopedia notes.
